author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
We're back with The Indie Hour Episode Fifteen! This series focuses on games you may have never even heard of and gives us an inside look at the wider world of independantly published Tabletop Wargames of all genres.

Do you love No Man's Sky? Subnautica? Just really like kit bashing monsters? Well have we got a game for you. SELECTED BY THE PATRONS. today we're checking out ALIEN ZOOLOGY. 

Check out ALIEN ZOOLOGY HERE: https://www.wargamevault.com/product/482988/Alien-Zoology-english-Open-Beta?affiliate_id=210041
title: The GMG Indie Hour Ep 015 - ALIEN ZOOLOGY
